40 miner trap by fire in gasp copper mine some 40 miner were trap underground today by a fire in a copper mine in the gasp area of eastern quebec , offici said . there were no report of ani death . a mine offici said that the fire broke out last night and about 25 of the miner made it to safeti . he said telephon contact had been establish with the trap miner but they could not be brought to the surfac until the fire wa extinguish . the caus of the fire wa not known .